videos.headline: Walton soars for Miami's 1st TD
videos.description: Miami RB Mark Walton rushes for a 5-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Rosier throws for 1st TD
videos.description: Miami QB Malik Rosier completes a 5-yard touchdown pass to WR Lawrence Cager.

videos.headline: Langham makes stellar grab for Miami TD
videos.description: Miami QB Malik Rosier throws a 5-yard touchdown pass to Darrell Langham to extend Miami's lead in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Walton's 2nd TD extends Miami's lead
videos.description: Miami RB Mark Walton rushes to the outside for a 6-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Jones fights for TD
videos.description: Bethune-Cookman RB Michael Jones rushes up the middle for a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Miami pads lead with Rosier's 3rd passing TD
videos.description: Miami QB Malik Rosier completes a 22-yard pass over the middle to Braxton Berrios for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Miami INT ends Bethune-Cookman's drive
videos.description: Miami DB Malek Young intercepts Larry Brihm Jr. pass in the end zone and returns it 24 yards.

videos.headline: Miami causes fumble with big hit
videos.description: Miami DB Amari Carter crushes Bethune-Cookman's Demetrius Weaver to cause a fumble.

videos.headline: Rosier's three TDs lead Miami past Bethune-Cookman
videos.description: Malik Rosier passes for 217 yards and three touchdowns in his starting debut to lead the Hurricanes past Bethune-Cookman 41-13.
